AR300Purgeara is a BusinessClass
    owned by ar
    prefix is W5356

    Patterns
        disable StaticTranslations
        implements WorkFile

    Persistent Fields
        WorkFile                is UniqueID
        WorkFileSeq             is Numeric size 12
        Company                 is like Company
        TransType               is Alpha size 1
        Invoice                 is like Invoice
        PaymentSeq              is like Sequence
        BatchNbr                is like BatchNumber
        AppSeq                  is like ApplicationSequence 
        Status                  is Numeric size 1
        AppldAmt                is like InternationalAmount
        AdjAmt                  is like InternationalAmount
        AdjSeq                  is like AdjustmentSequence
        CrCompany               is like Company 
        CrCustomer              is like Customer    
        CrBatch                 is like CrBatch
        CrPymntSeq              is like CrPymntSeq 
        CrType                  is like CrType
        CrNbr                   is like CrNbr	 
        	holds pii
        CrSuffix                is like Suffix
        CrCancelSeq             is Numeric size 4
        CrAppSeq                is like CrAppSeq 
        CrAppAmt                is like InternationalAmount
        CrOrigApAmt             is like InternationalAmount
        CrAdjSeq                is Numeric size 3
        CrAdjAmt                is like InternationalAmount
        DepositDate             is Date    
        OprCode                 is like ReceivableOperator  
        GlDate                  is Date    
        ArCode                  is like ReceivableGeneralLedgerCode
        OffsetCode              is like ReceivableGeneralLedgerCode
        AppSource               is Alpha size 1
        ResultFl                is like ResultFl
        OrigAppAmt              is like InternationalAmount
        AppCurrCd               is like Currency
        AppCurr                 is Alpha size 1
        ReverseFl               is Boolean
        PrepayFlag              is like Prepayment
        DeleteFl                is Alpha size 1

    Sets

        InsertionOrderSet
            indexed
            no duplicates
            primary
            Sort Order
                WorkFile
                WorkFileSeq

    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

            Field Rules
                WorkFileSeq
                    autosequence

        Delete is a Delete Action

        DeleteAll is a Set Action
            restricted

            Parameters
                WorkFileHeader is UniqueID

            Instance Selection
                where (WorkFile = WorkFileHeader)

            Local Fields
                LWorkFileHeader is a WorkFile

            Parameter Rules
                WorkFileHeader
                    required
                    LWorkFileHeader = WorkFileHeader

            Action Rules
                Instance Rules
                    invoke Delete

                Empty Set Rules
                    invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader

                Set Rules
                    Exit Rules
                        invoke Purge LWorkFileHeader
